## Description {#details}

A pack expansion.

Below this node, there are some unexpanded ParameterPacks which each have Child-&gt;ParameterPackSize elements.

Definition at line 1480 of file <a href="/docs/api/files/include/include/llvm/include/llvm/demangle/itaniumdemangle-h">ItaniumDemangle.h</a>.
